title: BONUS EPISODE - Quarantine Talk w/ Joey Cahill (6131 Records)
itunes:title: BONUS EPISODE - Quarantine Talk w/ Joey Cahill (6131 Records)
description:
In this weeks BONUS episode, I have my good friend Joey Cahill from 6131 Records on the show to discuss how this new reality is affecting him, his label and we discuss the implications to the music industry as a whole and where that could leave the insanely busy 2020 fall touring/festival schedule.
